      "options": {
        "code": { "language": "plaintext", "showLineNumbers": false, "showMiniMap": false },
        "content": "Use the chat at **http://localhost**, then **click any cell in Recent turns** to load the trace below. Expand the row in **Turn waterfall** to see spans. For the classic Gantt waterfall, use **Waterfall in Explore** on the trace ID. You can also paste a trace ID in **Turn trace** (top bar) and press **Enter**.",
